                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-4">
                                <div class="box blue">
                                    <div class="box-top">
                                       <h5 class="item">Calculator</h5> 
                                       <button  type="button" class="btn btn-success seccbut item"><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i></button>
                                    </div>
                                    <p>Uses data from past projects to provide better delivery estimates</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-4">
